 Dil to Pagal Hai (U)

 Yet another blockbuster from the maker of Silsila, Chandni and Darr. His third movie with the then rising star Shah Rukh Khan redefined candyfloss romance in couture garb. The movie also starred the yet-to -be Mrs Nene and fresh-as-a-flower Karisma Kapoor. 

 Channel check SET MAX on September 4 at 8 pm

